          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-4 mb-2">3.3 效果說明</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700">
            <li>不承諾增值空間</li>
            <li>不保證投資回報</li>
            <li>購買需謹慎，建議理性消費</li>
